MID_支援_オーディン_カミラ_Ｃ: $t1$Wmカミラ|7$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|$w0|…………$k\n$Wmオーディン|3$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,|$w0|Lady Camilla, what's the matter?\nYou have a dark expression...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|...Odin. No, nothing's wrong.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E苦,|Is that so. Well that's good...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,|Anyway, what are you doing here?\nDo you need me for something?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E通常,|Ah, that's right.\nThere's something I want to ask you.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaWell, go ahead and ask.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$Eキメ,|Your armor...what is its name?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,汗|Huh? Why? Do you want to wear it?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E苦,|Wear...!? I-I've never considered the idea...\nBut, if that idea were to become reality...$k$p$Eキメ,|If I wore that armor, from yonder sky\nmay I encounter gliding angels...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|Odin? What are you mumbling about?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E苦,|Huh?! Ah, no...it's nothing!\nMy attention was just entranced by nothing.$k$p$Eキメ,|The truth is, I've always been interested\nin something. Your cool armor!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,汗|Cool...armor? This?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,|Yes! That distinctive jet black...\nIts unique shape...it's flawless!$k$p$Eキメ,|What kind of sublime name\nis attached to such an armor...$k$pEven just thinking about it,\nmy spirit aches!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|Hmm, if you're talking about naming,\nit doesn't have a special name...$k\n$Wsオーディン|$WaI-is that so...?! That's...such a shame.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|If that's the case, you can\ncome up with a name for it.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,|Huh, really! Is that okay?!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yes, I think that you can definitely come up\nwith a good name. I look forward to it, Odin.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yes!$k
MID_支援_オーディン_カミラ_Ｂ: $t1$Wmオーディン|3$Wmカミラ|7$Wsオーディン|$Wa$Eキメ,|$w0|Lady Camilla!\nI've thought of a name for your armor.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|Aah...I've been waiting. Let's hear it.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,|Yes. Once and for all,\nthe name of the armor is...$k$p$Eキメ,|The buxomness that received\na blessing from the moon god...$k$p"Großartig Mont"!...\nHow's that?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|"Gros..." What...?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,|Großartig Mont.$k$p$E苦,|About that armor's image,\nI meditated upon it in a dark abyss...$k$p$E笑,|Then, two phrases\ndescended in my heart.$k$pThe first was "splendor". It means\njust that its richness is beautiful.$k$pThe second is "moon god".\nIt means a lunar spirit.$k$pI received the insane fusion of these two\nphrases...and its manifestation was...$k$p$Eキメ,|The celestial name...\n"Großartig Mont"!!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,|…………$k$pI see. Well, that's good.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E苦,|Huh? Nonono～!\nThat's good...aren't you too unconcerned?$k$p$Eキメ,|Argue about it a bit more!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|Argue? Why? I think it's a wonderful name.\nThat's why arguing is unnecessary...$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E苦,|R-really...?$k$p$E怒,| The name was just so suitable,\nyou think it's fine?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yes, of course.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E苦,|…………$k$pCould it be that the first one was decided,\nI've made a great miscalculation...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,|Hm? What's that paper\nyou have in your hand?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$Eキメ,|This, these are some other possibilities\nfor the name of your armor.$k$pRoughly, I thought up\none hundred and twenty.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|O-one hundred and twenty?!$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,|Yes. Among all these I thought there\nmust be one that you liked...$k$pBut it's unnecessary.\nB-but, it's absolutely not a problem!$k$p$Eキメ,|The other one hundred and nineteen\nwill be hurled into a place far away!!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,汗|R-really? I'm sorry. But, thank you Odin.\nThat you did this for me, I'm very happy.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E笑,|No, this is nothing!$k
MID_支援_オーディン_カミラ_Ａ: $a$t1$Wmオーディン|3$Wmカミラ|7$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|$w0|Ah, Odin. Thank you for earlier.$k$pI spoke with $Nu about my armor's\nname, who then said it really suited me.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E笑,|R-really?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yes. That's not a lie.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E苦,|…………$k$pWhat an honor...\nFor a name I made to be praised like this...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,汗|W-what's wrong?! Odin, are you crying?!$k\n$Wsオーディン|$WaN-no...these aren't tears.$k$p$Eキメ,|These are lazy fugitives...\nOr by another name, "Rage Getaway".$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|I-I see...$k$p$E通常,|At any rate, thank you, Odin.$k$p$E怒,|You've troubled yourself for me.$k$pAs a member of the royal family, I should\nbe working for the sake of the kingdom...$k$p$E笑,|But, because you've named my armor, I have\nan idea about the right path I should take.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa...Huh? Is that the case?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaThis armor is Großartig Mont.\nA beautiful moon spirit resides in it...$k$pSo thinking like this,\nI feel like the armor is like a part of me...$k$p$Eキメ,|As a soldier and as a member of the royal\nfamily, now I can see who I'm meant to be.$k$pIt's thanks to you, Odin.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,|…………$k$p$Eキメ,|Ha...!\nHahahahahahaha...$k$pThis joy seems to stretch\ntowards the distant horizon...$k$pThe almighty jet black fallen angels...they\nhave bestowed upon me their crimson joy.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,汗|Odin?\nAre you still mumbling to yourself?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E苦,|Ah. Sorry. My consciousness was\ninvited into a delightful garden...$k$p$E通常,|But... *sigh*\nThat's a relief...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,|Why?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,|May I disclose something to you,\nLady Camilla?$k$p$E苦,|The truth is...I've been troubled. Recently,\nI just couldn't think of any good names.$k$pBut because you immediately\naccepted your Großartig Mont...$k$p$E笑,|Somehow my self-confidence has returned!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|Well...! That's good.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$Eキメ,|*sigh*\n.........$k$pNow that my power is unlimited, the chosen\none's power that exceeds the world...$k$pIt releases the vibrantly colored light,\nand once more his body rises...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Hahaha...you're an interesting person.\nAttaboy.$k$pAnd from now on, if you're\nfeeling troubled, just talk to me.$k$pI'll listen to whatever\nyou have to say.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E笑,|Really?! Yes, thank you very much!\nI look forward to it, Lady Camilla!$k
MID_支援_オーディン_カミラ_Ｓ: $a$t1$Wmオーディン|3$Wmカミラ|7$w0|$Wsカミラ|$WaOdin, what is it?\nIf you have something to say, I'll listen...$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E苦,|N-no...\nThat's...the...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaCould it be, you've lost\nyour confidence again?$k$p$E笑,|Actually, I talked to our comrades\nabout my armor's name.$k$pAfter that, everyone wants you\nto name their clothes and weapons.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$WaIs that so...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,汗|...What's this? You're not pleased?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,|It's an honor but, I must refuse.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|Why...?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,汗|Normally, I'd be overjoyed to accept.\nBut now it's different.$k$p$E苦,|For our comrades,\nno good names are coming to mind...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|I see...$k$pSo you've been unable to\ncome up with clever names?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,|Yes...\nThe reason...is you, Lady Camilla.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,汗|Huh? M-me...?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$Eキメ,|To come up with Großartig Mont,\nI had to think deeply about you.$k$p$E怒,|For other people...\nI can't do the same.$k$pThere is no one who can readily\nmatch your wonderful character...$k$pSo I can't come up\nwith anything for them.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|Huh? Odin...\nThat...$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$Eキメ,照|Yes! I love you!\nWhen I called you here...$k$pI actually...wanted to\nconvey these feelings to you.$k$pLady Camilla...\nPlease accept this.$k$pTo connect us...a bridge of crimson dawn.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,|This is...a wedding ring?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,照|Yes. I want to marry you.\nTo say this, I called you here.$k$p$E怒,|But, if you want to reject me\ngo ahead and do it firmly.$k$pI'm prepared for the worst.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaReject? Why do you say that?$k$p$E笑,照|I'm incredibly happy.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E苦,照|...Huh?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,照|Hahaha...I want kids, you know.$k$pSince it's you, you'll come up\nwith wonderful names in a flash.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E怒,照|Huh? H-h-huh?\nThat's...$k$pNot coming up names as a normal\nparent, but as your husband...?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|Yes, that's what I mean.\nI'm in your care.$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E通常,照|Wah...\nR-really! I really thought I'd be rejected!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,照|Hahaha. Looking at you makes\nme yearn for motherhood.$k$pAside from $Nu, another person\nhas made me feel this way...$k$pAh, my beloved...will you\nbe with me from now on?$k\n$Wsオーディン|$Wa$E笑,照|Y-yes! I'm incredibly happy! Since you want\nit, I'll think of lots of names for children!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|I'm glad. Well then, let's go to the others.\nHand in hand, let's announce our marriage.$k
